ClassDecl.Name: GuiResourceFolder
ClassDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Resource folder. A resource folder contains many sub folders and sub items.</summary> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetImportUri
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the import uri for this folder.</summary> <returns>The import uri for this folder. Returns an empty string for non-import folders</returns> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: SetImportUri
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Set the import uri for this folder.</summary> <param name="uri">The import uri for this folder. Set an empty string for non-import folders</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetItem
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the item of a specified name.</summary> <returns>The item of a specified name.</returns> <param name="name">The specified name.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: AddItem
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Add a resource item.</summary> <returns>Returns true if this operation succeeded.</returns> <param name="name">The name of this resource item.</param> <param name="item">The resource item.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: RemoveItem
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Remove a resource item of a specified name.</summary> <returns>Returns the removed resource item if this operation succeeded.</returns> <param name="name">The name of this resource item.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetFolder
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the folder of a specified name.</summary> <returns>The folder of a specified name.</returns> <param name="name">The specified name.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: AddFolder
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Add a resource folder.</summary> <returns>Returns true if this operation succeeded.</returns> <param name="name">The name of this resource folder.</param> <param name="folder">The resource folder.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: RemoveFolder
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Remove a resource folder of a specified name.</summary> <returns>Returns the removed resource folder if this operation succeeded.</returns> <param name="name">The name of this resource folder.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetValueByPath
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get a contained resource object using a path like "Packages\Application\Name".</summary> <returns>The containd resource object.</returns> <param name="path">The path.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetFolderByPath
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get a resource folder using a path like "Packages\Application\Name\".</summary> <returns>The resource folder.</returns> <param name="path">The path.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: CreateValueByPath
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Create a contained resource object using a path like "Packages\Application\Name".</summary> <returns>Returns true if this operation succeeded.</returns> <param name="path">The path.</param> <param name="typeName">The type name of this contained object.</param> <param name="value">The contained object.</param> </Document>
